text:
The new costumes…
They should be arriving soon, right?

Yeah. That's right, I'm pretty sure──
They should be arriving at the office tomorrow.

…Haha
Tenka, you're looking forward to it, huh?

When we all wear matching outfits…
It somehow… gets Tenka fired up…!

Ah──
It's not like the others… aren't important too…!

When they arrive, please… let me know right away…
Tenka… want to try them on quickly…!
